Package: pidgin-sipe
Section: net
Architecture: any
Depends: gstreamer1.0-plugins-ugly, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: gstreamer1.0-libav, gstreamer1.0-x, remmina-plugin-rdp
Description: Pidgin plugin for Skype for Business and Microsoft Lync
 A third-party plugin for the Pidgin multi-protocol instant messenger.
 It implements the extended version of SIP/SIMPLE used by various products:
 .
     * Microsoft Skype for Business
     * Microsoft Lync
     * Microsoft Office Communications Server (OCS 2007/2007 R2 and newer)
     * Microsoft Live Communications Server (LCS 2003/2005)
     * Reuters Messaging
 .
 With this plugin you should be able to replace your Lync/SfB client with
 Pidgin.
